{"tid":2402641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟外交官、加國領館職員旁聽","createTime":"2021-02-10T14:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T14:11:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b7a1ff6dfdcb8c1222d110f1e9d33b2e96357d","tid":2402641,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/XQPUWZLPT5EJTCTU7EEAP3UMWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FXQPUWZLPT5EJTCTU7EEAP3UMWU%2F&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=23f5d85e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FXQPUWZLPT5EJTCTU7EEAP3UMWU%2F&h=f1fd9489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/XQPUWZLPT5EJTCTU7EEAP3UMWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟外交官、加國領館職員旁聽<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】黎智英保釋上訴案受到國際社會關注，亦有公眾人士前來聲援黎。早上8時半法院外已有近30人輪候公眾席，當中包括加拿大領事館職員及歐盟外交官、天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機等。散庭後黎智英被押上囚車返回赤柱監獄，支持者高呼「黎生加油」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：羅傑斯轟鄭若驊再次出賣港人<br />\n<br />\n終審法院昨就律政司覆核黎智英的保釋申請頒下判詞，多名泛民人士到場聲援。社民連主席黃浩銘聯同成員「長毛」梁國雄在庭外舉起寫上「言論無罪、打壓可恥」的橫額；另有約十名建制陣營的組織成員在示威區舉紙牌及叫喊口號，有數十名警員在庭外維持秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aQ7aTQGBIlbRlhUE2m9T-WdTeYs=/2138x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3QZVE3YNOJAG7BNNTGBLZKIF6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaQ7aTQGBIlbRlhUE2m9T-WdTeYs%3D%2F2138x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3QZVE3YNOJAG7BNNTGBLZKIF6E.jpg&h=e3bbaa75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■加拿大領事館職員（左）及歐盟外交官（右）到法院旁聽黎智英保釋上訴案。夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逾30人排隊輪候聽審<br />\n<br />\n上次聆訊有多名排頭位的南亞裔人士取籌後便離開未有聽審，旁聽人士昨日提早到場輪候公眾席，早上8時半已有近30人排隊，有人手持「釋放政治犯」紙皮文宣的躺在地上休息，人龍裏，包括加拿大領事館職員及歐盟駐香港辦事處副主任Charles Whiteley。據了解該歐盟代表上次因南亞排隊黨而未能入庭旁聽，昨日特意提早到場。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：梁家傑：日後保釋需更辣條件<br />\n<br />\n一名自稱「廢老」的男子昨早到場旁聽，他認為政府想殺雞儆猴，希望黎繼續堅持，「佢（黎智英）嘅公義自由、良知，所有香港人都會撐佢」。王婆婆則前晚6時便已排隊輪候。她舉起黃色雨傘及中英並列的「釋放政治犯」標語聲援黎，認為入場支持「多一個人好過少一個人」。<br />\n<br />\n至早上近10時，輪候旁聽的公眾人士陸續入庭，有人舉起五一手勢，社民連梁國雄則高叫「釋放政治犯」，壹傳媒行政總裁張劍虹亦有到場旁聽。黎智英其後由囚車押送到場，並在六名懲教人員陪同下步出囚室。<br />\n<br />\n法院最終裁定黎智英須繼續還柙，近11時，黎智英步出法院外上囚車，支持者包括王婆婆都高叫「黎生加油」，他們又安慰黎智英的家人，大叫「撐住」、「加油」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SF5oT-68YPX4zBo15beoxohyzO4=/1208x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZTM26TEMMNDOLNJTFP2TC4UL3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSF5oT-68YPX4zBo15beoxohyzO4%3D%2F1208x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZTM26TEMMNDOLNJTFP2TC4UL3I.jpg&h=80d496d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳日君樞機提早到場輪候公眾席時看書打發時間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QLnTWBLLBP1Y4P8B7kq9j03_8hQ=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQLnTWBLLBP1Y4P8B7kq9j03_8hQ%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.&h=721a3811&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XKSXPQQSCNDXPEA7IYDJ3YF6FM.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXKSXPQQSCNDXPEA7IYDJ3YF6FM.jpg&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=e7479f84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XKSXPQQSCNDXPEA7IYDJ3YF6FM.jpg</a><br />\n■《蘋果日報》副社長陳沛敏（左）及蘋果動新聞平台總監張志偉（右）向載着黎的囚車揮手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C08rgL-1ywXsNy8lvGXWzOuVyos=/1165x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IVSDL3LLM5CFFEJ6YUEKBPQ2GY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC08rgL-1ywXsNy8lvGXWzOuVyos%3D%2F1165x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIVSDL3LLM5CFFEJ6YUEKBPQ2GY.jpg&h=aa199c31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王婆婆手持「釋放所有政治犯」的標語支持黎智英。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5ilUN2v2YcN2OystuvknJ-J-UFg=/645x374/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q3GEHH7I5FHZDCYKW5TJY6BETA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5ilUN2v2YcN2OystuvknJ-J-UFg%3D%2F645x374%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ3GEHH7I5FHZDCYKW5TJY6BETA.gif&h=6a323ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英的子女到庭旁聽。左起：長子黎見恩、次子黎耀恩及女兒。"}]}